50|$|Islam {{was spread}} by the Salar {{people to the}} {{formerly}} Buddhist Kargan <b>Tibetans</b> in Lamo-shan-ken. Some <b>Tibetans</b> in Qinghai who converted to Islam are now considered Hui people.|$|R
